Kids Smart Watch

Watch for Kids Toys for 3-12 years old boys and girls

Multi-function smart watch for kids

Color: Purple, Blue, Black, Pink, Green, White

Size: Watch strap length: 230mm/9.4

Watch strap width: 20mm/0.79"

Camera: 0.3 MP pixel digital camera

Wristband: Silicone

Pls Note: Don't Support SIM Card, this kids smart watch don't support calling function

Music Player

Kids watch come with SD card, If want more music, you can download it from your computer via USB (save the mp3 file to "My Music Folder" on the Micro SD card).

24 Fun Games

Kids smart watch built-in 24 educational games helps kids learn through playing also can effectively exercise children's reaction ability and hand-eye coordination. Parents can set the game time to prevent children from being addicted.

Photo & Video Magic POP Sticker

Smart watch for kids come with a high-definition camera and cute special effects magic stickers, Record every wonderful moment in children's life.

3 Alarm 12/24 Hours and Calendar

Kids watch toys support alarm clock, 12/24H, Calendar. The kids smart watch can set 3 alarms to make children do own things on time, let them keep a strong sense of time.

Pedometer

Kids fitness traker with a pedometer counts kids steps and calories, and it will help your child develop positive health habits from kids.

Flashlight

Kids smartwatch with Flashlight

Built-in LED lights can provide lighting and safety warnings when where there is no light.

Tips:

1. Please fully charge this kids smart watch before first use (About 2 hours for a full charge).

2. If the watch stopped working, wont charge, or screen broken, etc. We would provide life-time friendly customer services.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
